~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : cloak                                     ~FTPODnuts Revision
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : cloak

   This will make you become cloaked so that other users cannot see
   you in the room, the "who" list, or the user count.  For all intents
   and purposes, you are completely invisible.  Coding has been added so
   that you may fake a login/logoff upon engaging/disengaging the cloak.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : invis, vis, who, look
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
